today. Did it look like it was a better opportunity 
than staying with Lone Star Gas? Well, it did to me,

00:22.486 --> 00:26.752
and of course, it was a very fortunate move for me. 
But I... For a period of time, I did wonder whether I

00:30.878 --> 00:40.429
had made a mistake, because it was a long way back 
for a company that had to get started. I could

00:41.190 --> 00:42.571
